content_description: Two friends are laughing hysterically in a hotel room, with one lying on the bed and the other sitting on the floor.

High.reason: Intense initial burst of laughter and dynamic camera movement between the two friends.

Medium.reason: One friend flexes his arm while laughing, showing moderate movement and engagement.

Low.reason: The laughter begins to subside as one friend sits up and starts to speak, showing calmer motion.
